# XXX : Old way
## setup shotMP.js for RPi Servie
http://www.instructables.com/id/Nodejs-App-As-a-RPI-Service-boot-at-Startup/

 - sudo npm install forever -g
 - cp shot-mp to /etc/init.d/
 - chmod 755 shot-mp
 - update-rc.d shot-mp defaults



